                            <comment id="13777882" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 18:38:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch changes rollWriterLock to be a ReentrantLock.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch keeps FSHLog#rollWriter() with priority over low replication checking. Boolean logRollRunning is removed since it is not needed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;18 iterations of TestLogRolling have passed against hadoop-2. Running 82 more iterations.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13777921" author="stack" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 19:01:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is a critical perf section.  Any measures done?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13778010" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 20:06:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the reminder.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch v2 shortens the duration which checkLowReplication() holds the lock by moving requestLogRoll() call out.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
